Class AbstractNativeIdentityChangePropagator

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.api.nativeidentitychange.AbstractNativeIdentityChangePropagator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativeIdentityChangePropagator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractNativeIdentityChangeRolePropagator, AccountNativeIdentityChangeIdentityPropagator, GroupNativeIdentityChangeIdentityPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeApplicationPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeCorrelationConfigPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeDynamicScopePropagator, NativeIdentityChangeFormPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeGenericPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeGroupDefinitionPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeIdentityTriggerPropagator, NativeIdentityChangePasswordPolicyHolderPropagator, NativeIdentityChangePolicyPropagator, NativeIdentityChangeRulePropagator
    public abstract class AbstractNativeIdentityChangePropagator
extends java.lang.Object
implements NativeIdentityChangePropagator
    Abstract base class that implements NativeIdentityChangePropagator. This provides default implementations for all the utility methods. Subclasses only need to implement NativeIdentityChangePropagator.processEvents(SailPointContext, List, TaskResult).
